{"tid":850074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 返工到歸西] 垃圾車停路中心　六旬司機昏倒車內　送院不治","createTime":"2018-10-06T07:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T09:46:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"864823c88593acae3b109d981e78065ce85813db","tid":850074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1941867/org/64f451f5110f8b7407348dd23aee3730.jpg/10_AKIioWaXlSD0Iv1lcUZgCOTxq5A99Y6vfi2Or34s?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1941867%2Forg%2F64f451f5110f8b7407348dd23aee3730.jpg%2F10_AKIioWaXlSD0Iv1lcUZgCOTxq5A99Y6vfi2Or34s%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=1c4e1754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周六（6日）清晨5時許，有途人路經何文田棗梨雅道近梭椏道對開時，發現一輛垃圾車停於馬路中央，查看下赫見一名65歲姓吳男司機，於車內不省人事，慌忙報警。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報趕抵，立即將男司機送往廣華醫院，當時他仍陷於昏迷，抵院搶救後終告不治。警方初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，列作有人暈倒送院前死亡，男事主死因有待驗屍後確定。事後，現場棗梨雅道需要封閉，交通輕微受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/243778/司機猝死-何文田垃圾車停路中心-六旬司機昏倒車內-送院不治\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F243778%2F%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E7%8C%9D%E6%AD%BB-%E4%BD%95%E6%96%87%E7%94%B0%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E8%BB%8A%E5%81%9C%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%98%8F%E5%80%92%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%A7-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB&d=tmnNc1%2F5Cp15QOcWwSiJjwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0ed7addd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/243778/司機猝死-何文田垃圾車停路中心-六旬司機昏倒車內-送院不治</a>"},{"pid":"11b860f76e7a361d02fede1117b8a37eda9d24d9","tid":850074,"uid":141164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"番工不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169d8ff455470da2db9cccc79e0b8aa32b5df41e","tid":850074,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T09:46:56.000Z","msg":"只有死亡先有真係既休息<img src=\"/